comments.body:
the headers object here would likely be some derivative of node's `http.IncomingHttpHeaders` where everything is optional, so if I make it not optional it would force some unnecessary checks or casting that is handled by the internals of the library anyway.

```ts
interface IncomingHttpHeaders {
        'accept'?: string;
        'accept-patch'?: string;
      // etc...
}
```

